### NduthiRide — Rides endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@userToken = <paste_user_access_token_here>
@riderToken = <paste_rider_access_token_here>
@rideId = <paste_ride_id_here>

### ─── Create a new ride booking (user) ──────────────────────
# @name createRide
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickupLat": -1.2921,
  "pickupLng": 36.8219,
  "pickupAddress": "Nairobi CBD, Kenyatta Avenue",
  "dropoffLat": -1.3000,
  "dropoffLng": 36.8500,
  "dropoffAddress": "Upper Hill, Nairobi",
  "paymentMethod": "MPESA",
  "mpesaPhone": "0712345678"
}

### Capture ride ID
@newRideId = {{createRide.response.body.data.id}}

### ─── Get my rides (user — paginated) ───────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/rides?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ─── Get a specific ride ────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ─── Accept a ride (rider) ──────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{riderToken}}

### ─── Update ride status (rider) ────────────────────────────
### Valid transitions: ACCEPTED → EN_ROUTE_TO_PICKUP → ARRIVED_AT_PICKUP → IN_PROGRESS → COMPLETED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{riderToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "EN_ROUTE_TO_PICKUP"
}

### ─── Cancel a ride (user or rider) ─────────────────────────
### Only PENDING or ACCEPTED rides can be cancelled
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ─── Rate a completed ride ──────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}/rate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 5,
  "comment": "Great ride, very professional!"
}

### ─── Get fare estimate ───────────────────────────────────────
### Estimate without creating a booking
GET {{baseUrl}}/rides/estimate?pickupLat=-1.2921&pickupLng=36.8219&dropoffLat=-1.3000&dropoffLng=36.8500
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
